title: X-Plane Payware Aircraft Diamond DA-42 (RTT designs)
description:
Ok, i got some Payware Aircraft for X-Plane in the last months and due to strong demand here on Piratebay i decided to share them with you guys.
So here&#039;s the first one, RTT Design&#039;s Diamond DA-42 TwinStar, a great twin engine five seater, which comes in 4 variation and with a WIndows, Mac and Linux Plug-In, compatible with all architectures as well as X-Plane 9.

Have fun and keep sharing, as i can&#039;t share for long.

Enjoy!
